Types

fnum = float
inum = int
Region2f = concept e
    bbox(e) is BBox2f
    inside(Vec2f, e) is bool
    dist(Vec2f, e) is fnum
    distSq(Vec2f, e) is fnum
Vec2[T] = tuple[x, y: T]
Vec2f = Vec2[fnum]
Vec2i = Vec2[inum]
Vec3[T] = tuple[x, y, z: T]
Vec3f = Vec3[fnum]
Vec3i = Vec3[inum]
Vec4[T] = tuple[x, y, z, w: T]
Vec4f = Vec4[fnum]
Vec4i = Vec4[inum]
Polar = tuple[r, theta: fnum]
Segment[T] = object
  st*, en*: T

Segment2f = Segment[Vec2f]
Segment2i = Segment[Vec2i]
Triangle[T] = array[3, T]
Triangle2f = Triangle[Vec2f]
Triangle3f = Triangle[Vec3f]
Rect2f = object
  origin*, size*: Vec2f

Path2f = seq[Vec2f]
Polygon2f = object
  contour: Path2f
  holes: seq[Path2f]

Circle2f = object
  center*: Vec2f
  r: fnum

BBox[T] = object
  min*, max*: T

BBox2[T] = BBox[Vec2[T]]
BBox2f = BBox[Vec2f]
BBox2i = BBox[Vec2i]
BBox3[T] = BBox[Vec3[T]]
BBox3f = BBox[Vec3f]
BBox3i = BBox[Vec3i]
Mat3x3[T] = array[3, array[3, T]]
Mat3x3f[T] = array[3, array[3, fnum]]
Orient = enum
  orCCW = -1, orCollinear = 0, orCW = 1

eps = 1e-010
